OL,3,CFarage: Restart coal mining and bring
OL,4,Cback traditional steelmaking to Wales
OL,6,FNigel Farage has called for the blast
OL,7,Ffurnaces at Port Talbot's steelworks
OL,8,Fto reopen as Reform UK sets its sights
OL,9,Fon the Welsh Senedd elections in 2026.
OL,11,FOn a visit to the town, the party
OL,12,Fleader said the resumption of
OL,13,Ftraditional steelmaking should be the
OL,14,Fambition.
OL,16,FFarage has also suggested some coal
OL,17,Fmines could re-open in Wales to power
OL,18,Fthe production of steel in Port Talbot.
