OL,3,CFarage: Restart coal mining and bring
OL,4,Cback traditional steelmaking to Wales
OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference, the
OL,7,FReform UK leader said he believes his
OL,8,Fparty has a chance of ending Labour's
OL,9,Flong-standing dominance in Wales
OL,10,Fduring the Senedd elections next May
OL,11,Famid opinion poll momentum and gains
OL,12,Fmade at the local polls last month.
OL,14,FThe Labour UK government has backed
OL,15,Fplans for a new #1.25 billion electric
OL,16,Farc furnace at the Tata steelworks,
OL,17,Fwith the switch-on due in 2027 as part
OL,18,Fof the push towards greener production.
