OL,3,CFarage: Restart coal mining and bring
OL,4,Cback traditional steelmaking to Wales
OL,6,FThe plant's last blast furnace was
OL,7,Fshut down in September 2024, and
OL,8,Fnearly 2,000 people in Port Talbot
OL,9,Fhave lost their jobs.
OL,11,FCriticising the government's current
OL,12,Fplans, Farage said: "The electric arc
OL,13,Fis fine for recycling steel, it
OL,14,Fdoesn't produce the virgin steel
OL,15,Fneeded for military hardware, but the
OL,16,Fproblem is that it uses vast amounts
OL,17,Fof electric in the the most expensive
OL,18,Findustrial electric prices in the
OL,19,Fworld.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/16
