OL,3,CFarage: Restart coal mining and bring
OL,4,Cback traditional steelmaking to Wales
OL,6,F"I very much doubt that furnace will
OL,7,Fever be switched on . Our ambition is
OL,8,Fto reindustrialise Wales. Our belief
OL,9,Fis that we should make our own steel.
OL,10,FOur belief is - for what uses coal
OL,11,Fstill has - we should use our own coal.
OL,13,F"I'm not saying let's open up all the
OL,14,Fpits, what I am saying is there are
OL,15,Fspecific types of coal for certain
OL,16,Fuses that we still need in this
OL,17,Fcountry and we need for the blast
OL,18,Ffurnaces here that we should produce
OL,19,Fourselves."
