OL,3,CFarage: Restart coal mining and bring
OL,4,Cback traditional steelmaking to Wales
OL,6,FTata Steel had been working to fully
OL,7,Fdecommission and strip most of the
OL,8,Firon and steelmaking assets across the
OL,9,FPort Talbot site by the end of 2024,
OL,10,Fleaving little possibility of
OL,11,Frestarting the blast furnaces in their
OL,12,Fcurrent form.
OL,14,FThe company said many of the existing
OL,15,F'heavy end' assets - such as blast
OL,16,Ffurnaces and coke ovens - had reached
OL,17,Fthe "end of their operational life."
