OL,3,CFarage: Restart coal mining and bring
OL,4,Cback traditional steelmaking to Wales
OL,6,FTata Steel CEO Rajesh Nair has
OL,7,Fpreviously said that there was "no
OL,8,Fway" the blast furnaces could be kept
OL,9,Fgoing, for both technical and
OL,10,Ffinancial reasons.
OL,12,FProfessor Cameron Pleydell-Pearce, a
OL,13,Fsteel expert and professor at Swansea
OL,14,FUniversity, told ITV Wales it would
OL,15,Fnot be as straightforward as simply
OL,16,Freopening the furnace in isolation,
OL,17,Fsaying that there would be a need to
OL,18,Fimport iron ore due to its low
OL,19,Favailability in the UK.
