OL,3,CFarage: Restart coal mining and bring
OL,4,Cback traditional steelmaking to Wales
OL,6,F"If you want to open any steel plant,
OL,7,Fyou're going to have to invest
OL,8,Fhundreds of millions, if not billions,
OL,9,Fdepending on the configuration that
OL,10,Fyou want.... Because we're in a
OL,11,Fposition where this furnace is going
OL,12,Fto be hard to restart, just from a
OL,13,Ftechnical perspective, it has to
OL,14,Ffactor into it as well. So it's not
OL,15,Fjust the investment that you're
OL,16,Fmaking, but the technical complexity
OL,17,Fof restarting."
