OL,3,CFarage: Restart coal mining and bring
OL,4,Cback traditional steelmaking to Wales
OL,6,FHe continued: "It's not impossible,
OL,7,Fbut the question is whether or not
OL,8,Fthat fits into the strategy that's
OL,9,Fright for the UK. We have an abundance
OL,10,Fof scrap in the UK, so a scrap-
OL,11,Frecycling strategy makes sense. In
OL,12,Fother locations, there are plentiful
OL,13,Fsupplies of iron ore and lower energy
OL,14,Fcosts, so it might make sense for
OL,15,Fthose locations to go with more ore-
OL,16,Fbased steelmaking."
