OL,6,FSpeaking about Farage's proposals,
OL,7,FChris Bryant, MP for the Rhondda and
OL,8,FOgmore, said: "This is really cruel
OL,9,Fpolitics from Nigel Farage, trying to
OL,10,Fpretend he's got a plan and he hasn't
OL,11,Fgot a plan at all.
OL,13,F"He couldn't afford what he's saying
