OL,3,CFarage: Restart coal mining and bring
OL,4,Cback traditional steelmaking to Wales
OL,6,FFarage's speech comes as Reform seeks
OL,7,Fto draw a line under internal clashes
OL,8,Fafter chairman Zia Yusuf quit the
OL,9,Fparty on Thursday only to return 48
OL,10,Fhours later, saying the resignation
OL,11,Fhad been "born out of exhaustion".
OL,13,FHe referenced this disagreement in his
OL,14,Fspeech saying: "We hit a speed bump-
OL,15,F it could've been that we were driving
OL,16,Fmore than 20mph", jibing at the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment's default speed limit
OL,18,Fpolicy - something he has pledged to
OL,19,Fscrap if Reform UK were in power in
OL,20,Fthe Senedd.
